  "primerModeTitle": "Three colours of scale",
  "primerModeMajor": "A major scale sounds bright and happy. Listen to it climb.",
  "primerModeMinor": "A minor scale sounds darker — its 3rd, 6th and 7th steps sit a little lower.",
  "primerModeDorian": "Dorian is like minor, but its 6th step is raised — so it sounds minor with a brighter twist. That one note is the whole secret!",
